room_title: Escape room "The Office: Race To Erase" by Amazing Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_description:
In a moment of impulsive anger, you’ve sent your boss an email that will surely get you fired. You show up to work expecting the worst, but your boss is nowhere to be found. Your coworker says the boss has a dentist’s appointment this morning, and that he will be in to work an hour late.
In a last-ditch effort to save your job, you must get into the boss’s office, delete the email and get out before the boss gets to work and reads it. Can you beat the clock and erase the email in time to keep your job?
